tracks.tag_list: Steve Moyse "Jake Aldidge" "Hip Hop" Rap Pop Unsigned Fresh Unique Dirty Dancing Country Suffolk UK Commercial Hybrid Jake Aldridge Urban ACJ Beats ITUNES Independent
tracks.title: Steve Moyse - DIRTY DANCING - feat. Jake Aldridge
tracks.description:
Dirty Dancing provides listeners with the ultimate hybrid, as Steve Moyse & Jake Aldridge fuse Hip Hop & Country music together. Dirty Dancing was produced by ACJ Beats & is currently signed to Leopard Music Publishing. 

Dirty Dancing is a Steve Moyse track, which features Jake Aldridge. The song was originally recorded back in 2010, but Steve & Jake decided to hold the release back, both artists felt the production on the track at that time was not at a good enough standard. Steve & Jake spent years trying to find a suitable producer who could do the song some justice. Many producers had a crack at remixing Dirty Dancing, but Steve and Jake were never blown away by what they heard.

In 2014, Jake contacted ACJ Beats and enquired about the possibility of having him remix the track. After sending him the Acappellas for the song, ACJ got to work on the track and Steve & Jake were amazed by what he sent back, it was at this point, the pair new the track was finally about to see the light of day - four years later. 

The track fuses a number of Genre's including R&B, Hip Hop, Country, Pop, & Dance.

For more information, please see the following links: 

www.jakealdridge.com
www.soundcloud.com/jakealdridge
